                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-26-victim351 t18321129-26-viclabel154"></join>. On the 3rd of November he came to me, and said Mr. Harris wanted 3l. to finish paying the girls in the factory, and produced a note, which is lost, saying "Let Walker have 3l.," and signed by Mr. Harris: I gave him three sovereigns out of the till - they belonged to my master.</p>
